text: Alaska Passage is a 1959 American drama movie directed by Edward Bernds and starring Bill Williams, Naura Hayden, Lyn Thomas, Leslie Bradley, Raymond Hatton. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1959 drama movies Category:American drama movies Category:Movies set in Alaska Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by Edward Bernds
